---
title: Claim Ingestion — Phase 1 (Ingestion → Detection → Entity Extraction)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant USER as Operator
    participant API as Consumer API
    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant OYDB as Orchestrator<br/>YottaDB
    participant ING as ingestion-agent<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant ING_YDB as ingestion-agent<br/>YottaDB
    participant ING_MIRTH as ingestion-agent<br/>Mirth
    participant DET as claim-detector<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant DET_YDB as claim-detector<br/>YottaDB
    participant ENT as entity-extractor<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant ENT_YDB as entity-extractor<br/>YottaDB
    participant OMIRTH as Orchestrator<br/>Mirth

    USER->>API: POST /claims<br/>{claim_text, source_url, source_date}

    API->>API: validate input<br/>sanitize PII<br/>assign claim_id + run_id

    API->>ORC: initiate_run({<br/>  run_id: "RUN-20260406-a3f7",<br/>  claim_id: "CLAIM-20260406-001",<br/>  claim_text: "...",<br/>  source_url: "...",<br/>  source_date: "20211104"<br/>})

    ORC->>OYDB: create run record<br/>^RUN(run_id, "status") = "INGESTED"<br/>^RUN(run_id, "expected_agent_count") = 10

    API-->>USER: 202 Accepted<br/>{run_id, status: "INGESTED",<br/>poll_url: "/runs/RUN-..."}

    Note over ORC,ING: Phase 1a — Ingestion

    ORC->>ING: MCP invoke_task({<br/>  run_id, claim_id,<br/>  claim_text, source_url, source_date<br/>})

    ING->>ING_YDB: tool: create_message()<br/>tool: set_entity()<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIM_TEXT, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIM_SOURCE_URL, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIM_SOURCE_DATE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIM_DOMAIN, F)

    ING->>ING_MIRTH: send HL7v2 ACK message

    ING_MIRTH->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK AA

    ORC->>OYDB: mark ingestion-agent COMPLETE<br/>^RUN(run_id, "terminal_obx_count") = 1

    Note over ORC,DET: Phase 1b — Claim Detection

    ORC->>DET: MCP invoke_task({<br/>  run_id, claim_text<br/>})

    DET->>DET: score check-worthiness<br/>normalize claim text

    DET->>DET_YDB: tool: add_observation(CHECK_WORTHY_SCORE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CLAIM_NORMALIZED, F)

    DET->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK via Mirth

    ORC->>ORC: evaluate CHECK_WORTHY_SCORE<br/>if score < 0.4 → transition to CANCELLED

    alt check_worthy_score >= 0.4
        ORC->>OYDB: status = "ANALYZING"
        Note over ORC,ENT: Phase 1c — Entity Extraction

        ORC->>ENT: MCP invoke_task({run_id, claim_text})

        ENT->>ENT: extract persons, orgs,<br/>dates, locations, statistics

        ENT->>ENT_YDB: tool: add_observation(ENTITY_PERSON, F) ×N<br/>tool: add_observation(ENTITY_ORG, F) ×N<br/>tool: add_observation(ENTITY_DATE, F) ×N<br/>tool: add_observation(ENTITY_LOCATION, F) ×N<br/>tool: add_observation(ENTITY_STATISTIC, F) ×N

        ENT->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK via Mirth

        ORC->>ORC: Phase 1 complete<br/>dispatch Phase 2 fan-out

    else check_worthy_score < 0.4
        ORC->>OYDB: status = "CANCELLED"
        ORC-->>API: run_status = CANCELLED<br/>reason = "Check-worthy score below threshold"
        API-->>USER: GET /runs/RUN-... → CANCELLED
    end
